"1 cup all-purpose flour","1/2 teaspoon baking soda","1/2 teaspoon ground cinnamon","1/4 teaspoon salt","1/2 cup plus 2 Tbsp. unsalted butter, softened","1/2 cup granulated sugar","1/2 cup firmly packed light brown sugar","1  large egg","1 teaspoon fiori di sicilia or orange extract (see note)","1 cup uncooked regular oats","8 ounces white chocolate, chopped (about 2 cups)","1/2 cup raisins or golden raisins"